# CODEOWNERS — midnightntwrk/servicedesk
#
# Default owners: @hegaleon and the @midnightntwrk/mn-sre team. The team
# co-ownership eliminates the previous single-point-of-failure on a single
# user for routine repo changes.
#
# Governance, security-policy and secret-touching files require both
# @midnightntwrk/mn-security and @midnightntwrk/mn-sre sign-off. The set
# below is standardized on the pattern used in other midnightntwrk repos
# (see midnightntwrk/midnight-node) and extended with the three workflows
# in this repo that hold live secrets / App credentials.

*                                           @hegaleon @midnightntwrk/mn-sre

# ── Governance + policy ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md                         @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/CODEOWNERS                                 @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/CONTRIBUTING.md                            @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/LICENSE                                    @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/SECURITY.md                                @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre

# ── GitHub config + scanning ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
/.github/dependabot.yml                     @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/                    @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE/             @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/.github/workflows/scan.yaml                @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre

# ── Secret-touching workflows (servicedesk-specific) ─────────────────────────
# p1-pagerduty.yml      — uses PAGERDUTY_ROUTING_KEY
# route-iac.yml         — uses IAC_APP_ID / IAC_APP_PRIVATE_KEY (GitHub App)
# route-shielded.yml    — reuses IAC_APP_ID / IAC_APP_PRIVATE_KEY for cross-org issue mirroring
/.github/workflows/p1-pagerduty.yml         @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/.github/workflows/route-iac.yml            @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
/.github/workflows/route-shielded.yml       @midnightntwrk/mn-security @midnightntwrk/mn-sre
